                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for extracting beryllium element from fluorite tailings",
                    "一种从萤石尾矿中提取铍元素的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a method for extracting beryllium from fluorite tailings, and relates to the technical field of fluorite tailings treatment. The method for extracting the beryllium element from the fluorite tailings specifically comprises the following steps of S1, grinding and leaching, S2, precipitating and separating, S3, roasting, S4, treating with a reducing agent, S5, reducing and S6, refining. The hydrogen sulfide gas generated in the roasting process is introduced into the carbon reducing agent for heating, so that enhanced application of hydrogen sulfide as the reducing agent is successfully realized, the measure is beneficial to energy saving and production cost reduction, the participation of hydrogen sulfide as the reducing agent can promote the reaction process and improve the reduction efficiency and the yield, and finally, the method is suitable for industrial production. And through comprehensive utilization of roasting waste gas, cyclic utilization of resources is achieved, and the concept of sustainable development is completely met."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供一种从萤石尾矿中提取铍元素的方法，涉及萤石尾矿处理技术领域。该萤石尾矿中提取铍元素的方法，具体包括以下步骤：S1.研磨和浸出，S2.沉淀和分离，S3.焙烧，S4.还原剂处理，S5.还原，S6.精炼。通过导入焙烧过程中产生的硫化氢气体至碳还原剂中进行加热，成功实现了将硫化氢作为还原剂的加强应用，这一举措不仅有助于节约能源、降低生产成本，而且硫化氢作为还原剂的参与能够促进反应过程，提升还原效率和产率，最终，通过对焙烧废气的综合利用，实现了资源的循环利用，这完全符合可持续发展的理念。"
                }
            ]
